{"tid":1700672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葛珮帆：對周梓樂離世感到非常心痛","createTime":"2019-11-08T15:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T17:08:14.000Z","uid":43839,"like":92,"dislike":201,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"a8eb08fb97bb2630ed9883505146858a05b21e14","tid":1700672,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>葛珮帆：對周梓樂離世感到非常心痛<br />\n08.11.2019 15:32<br />\n立法會內務委員會召開第五次會議，選舉正副主席。會議開始時，主持會議的公民黨郭榮鏗提出，為墮樓死亡的科大學生周梓樂默哀3分鐘。多名民主派議員手持白花，胸前戴上白絲帶站立，議會秘書亦有站立默哀。建制派方面，民建聯蔣麗芸和經民聯張華峰離開，無人留在會議室參與默哀。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯葛珮帆表示，她對周梓樂離世亦感到非常心痛，並希望警方盡快徹查事件。<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">她又指，議會的規矩一直不容許有默哀儀式</span></span></strong></em></span></ins>，不參與儀式不代表議員不痛心。按照議會慣例，立法會主席可命令或容許默哀，向在任議員、與立法會有密切關係的人，或曾對香港作出重大貢獻人士的逝世表示哀悼，而內會亦可進行默哀。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1205030&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1205030%26csid%3D261_341&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=f73dd607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1205030&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n其實係咁,議會係唔係真係有&quot;不容許有默哀儀式&quot; 我就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我相信默哀都係幾分鐘既事,成班建制拉隊走人,你搵個咁藉口同火上加油無分別<br />\n既然葛博士咁守規矩,咁我又搵下議會有無試過默哀,點知葛博士今天的自己打倒上年既自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUcHhDp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUcHhDp.jpg&h=8def0904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180114/20274058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F20274058&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=ada5ac3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F20274058&h=6b7d1c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180114/20274058</a><br />\n<br />\n上年先有默哀,咁我咪查下出席表邊個咁唔守規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一查,喂葛博士係度喎,咁緊係睇下佢有無閃人啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PyOCQZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPyOCQZu.jpg&h=1793e72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzWwVsq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzWwVsq.jpg&h=59b00e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以佢下面link 睇片&quot;14:37:25&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/hc/sub_com/hs101/agenda/hs10120180113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr16-17%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fsub_com%2Fhs101%2Fagenda%2Fhs10120180113.htm&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=7eb3ba95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/hc/sub_com/hs101/agenda/hs10120180113.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葛博士你搵個藉口都搵好啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68936c00c894d5c203814feadb7cc5d1cfa1e6b3","tid":1700672,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">幫手入黎Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n【英美戰線】我淨係知，唔可以輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700470</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2449c5b1cc82744854e1ec07cbcb2fd063919db1","tid":1700672,"uid":1049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:36:18.000Z","msg":"屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ae93a44985886c02c8cd54b34b51df493b4891","tid":1700672,"uid":